            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-guides-hub/1100-6529183/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6529183">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>A vast realm awaits you in <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/kingdom-come-deliverance-ii/" data-ref-id="5000-625869"><strong>Kingdom Come: Deliverance 2</strong></a>, sequel to the 2018 open-world adventure role-playing game (RPG) from Warhorse Studios. This sequel continues the journey of Henry of Skalitz across war-torn Bohemia, where you encounter friends and foes, both fresh and familiar, in an unforgettable adventure that's equal parts compelling, remarkable, and frustrating to boot. Here's our Kingdom Come: Deliverance 2 guides hub to help you as you get started.</p><div data-embed-type="toc"><p><span><strong>Table of Contents</strong> [<a data-toggle="collapse" href="#toc_list">hide</a>]</span></p><ul id="toc_list"><li><a href="#Kingdom_Come__Deliverance_2_guides_hub">Kingdom Come: Deliverance 2 guides hub</a><ul><li><a href="#General_gameplay_mechanics">General gameplay mechanics</a></li><li><a href="#Characters_and_companions">Characters and companions</a></li><li><a href="#Skills_guides">Skills guides</a></li><li><a href="#Quests_and_progression">Quests and progression</a></li></ul></li></ul></div><h2 id="Kingdom_Come__Deliverance_2_guides_hub">Kingdom Come: Deliverance 2 guides hub</h2><p>Our Kingdom Come: Deliverance 2 guides hub is organized into multiple categories depending on related mechanics and themes. We tackle everything from basic concepts to expansive quest chains.</p><h3 id="General_gameplay_mechanics">General gameplay mechanics</h3><p>From one corner of Bohemia to the next, Henry of Skalitz has his work cut out for him. Given that this is a sequel, several systems are derived from the original game, though there are vast improvements, too. We talk about some of the basics that you're likely to encounter within the first few hours of starting the campaign.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-how-long-to-beat-campaign-quest-list/2900-6187/" data-ref-id="2900-6187">Campaign length and missions: How long does it take to beat the game?</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-fast-travel-locations-world-map-guide/2900-6216/" data-ref-id="2900-6216">All fast travel locations and full world map</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-fast-travel-regions-trosky-kuttenberg-suchdol/2900-6186/" data-ref-id="2900-6186">How to fast travel between regions</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-dice-game-farkle-tips-guide/2900-6189/" data-ref-id="2900-6189">How to win at Farkle (dice game)</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-badges-unique-dice/2900-6190/" data-ref-id="2900-6190">Where to find unique badges and dice</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-food-cook-smoke-dry/2900-6191/" data-ref-id="2900-6191">Food guide: Should you cook, smoke, or dry your meats?</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-heal-character-hp-guide/2900-6192/" data-ref-id="2900-6192">How to heal your character</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-save-game-guide/2900-6194/" data-ref-id="2900-6194">How to save the game</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-savior-schnapps-guide/2900-6195/" data-ref-id="2900-6195">How to get more Savior Schnapps</a></li></ul><h3 id="Characters_and_companions">Characters and companions</h3><p>Your journey is fraught with dangers, but you don't have to go at it alone. Many allies are willing to lend a helping hand, including animal companions that you're likely to feel attached to over time. And, of course, you might turn folks--femmes and fellahs--into new flames or flirtatious trysts.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-romance-sex-scenes-guide/2900-6196/" data-ref-id="2900-6196">Characters: Romance options</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-mutt-loyalty-dog-companion/2900-6199/" data-ref-id="2900-6199">Animal companions: Mutt the Dog</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-horse-mount-pebbles/2900-6197/" data-ref-id="2900-6197">Animal companions: Pebbles and other horses</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-horse-items-saddle/2900-6198/" data-ref-id="2900-6198">Animal companions: How to equip horse armor</a></li></ul><h3 id="Skills_guides">Skills guides</h3><p>As you progress further into the campaign as Henry, you make the most out of an assortment of gameplay systems. Many of these are tied to skills and attributes, whether it's using your gift of gab to get out of sticky situations (or to find yourself in one), or sneaking around at night and robbing people to make yourself rich.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-reset-skills-perks-guide/2900-6193/" data-ref-id="2900-6193">General: How to reset skills and perks</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-carry-weight-encumbrance/2900-6188/" data-ref-id="2900-6188">Strength: How to increase carry weight</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-charisma-speech-skill-checks/2900-6202/" data-ref-id="2900-6202">Speech and Charisma: How to pass dialogue skill checks</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-alchemy-potions-guide/2900-6200/" data-ref-id="2900-6200">Alchemy: How to brew potions</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-stealth-thievery-pickpocket-steal/2900-6203/" data-ref-id="2900-6203">Stealth and Thievery: How to sneak and steal from people</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-lockpicks-lockpicking-guide/2900-6201/" data-ref-id="2900-6201">Stealth and Thievery: How to get more lockpicks</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-guns-ammo-hand-cannon/2900-6204/" data-ref-id="2900-6204">Marksmanship: How to get a gun</a></li></ul><h3 id="Quests_and_progression">Quests and progression</h3><p>Kingdom Come: Deliverance 2 features expansive quest chains that offer players a lot of freedom. There are numerous optional objectives to tackle, as well as skill checks that determine how you approach each task. Some of these moments are also tense and exciting, where making mistakes at crucial points can be downright disastrous.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-wedding-crashers/2900-6212/" data-ref-id="2900-6212">Main quest: Wedding Crashers</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-hans-for-whom-the-bell-tolls/2900-6213/" data-ref-id="2900-6213">Main quest: For Whom the Bell Tolls</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-storm-istvan-toth/2900-6215/" data-ref-id="2900-6215">Main quest: Storm</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-do-not-publish-1/2900-6206/" data-ref-id="2900-6206">Main quest: Taking French Leave</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-lackey-vostatek/2900-6210/" data-ref-id="2900-6210">Side quest: Lackey</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-pavlena-bad-blood/2900-6211/" data-ref-id="2900-6211">Side quest: Bad Blood</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/kingdom-come-deliverance-2-demons-of-trosky/2900-6214/" data-ref-id="2900-6214">Side quest: Demons of Trosky</a></li></ul><p>We'll continue to add more articles to our Kingdom Come: Deliverance 2 guides hub, so stay tuned.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
