                <p>With the <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/switch-2-release-date-specs-display-price/1100-6520278/">Switch 2</a> launching this year, Nintendo has confirmed that it is preparing to prevent scalpers from negatively impacting the release of its hybrid console. In a press conference, Nintendo president Shuntaro Furukawa said that the company would take all "possible measures" for the Switch 2 to produce enough stock to meet demand.</p><p>"We will take all possible measures based on the experience we have accumulated to date," Furukawa said to <a href="https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUF31BM40R30C25A1000000/" rel="nofollow ">Nikkei</a> (via <a href="https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/nintendo-says-its-making-preparations-for-switch-2-resellers/" rel="nofollow ">VGC</a>). "We are making preparations."</p><div tabindex="0" data-id="1554077888" data-promo-id="0" data-user-has-ads="1" data-video="{&quot;id&quot;:6465596,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Nintendo%20Switch%202%20%E2%80%93%20Official%20First%20Look%20Reveal%20Trailer&quot;,&quot;lengthSeconds&quot;:141,&quot;startTime&quot;:0,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;share&quot;:{&quot;linkUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/nintendo-switch-2-official-first-look-reveal-trailer\/2300-6465596\/&quot;,&quot;embedUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465596\/&quot;,&quot;embedHtml&quot;:{&quot;640&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465596\/\&quot; height=\&quot;360\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\/iframe>&quot;,&quot;480&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465596\/\&quot; height=\&quot;270\&quot; width=\&quot;480\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\